    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "OFLYING DISCS, MISCELLANEOUS",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "On September 26, 1949, [REDACTED], S. Charleston,",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "West Virginia, appeared at the Charleston, West Virginia resident agency and",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "gave to Special Agent [REDACTED] the attached letter. Mr. [REDACTED] stated",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "that he had written the letter following a pleasure flight from Clark Field,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "St. Albans, West Virginia, to Parkersburg, West Virginia, on September 25,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "1949. Mr. [REDACTED] stated that after writing the letter, he did not know",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "whether it would be of any interest to the FBI and decided that instead of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "mailing it directly to the Bureau at Washington, he would contact the local",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "agent and turn it over to him if it were thought it would be of interest to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "the Bureau.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] stated that he has set out the complete details of this",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "incident in his letter and that there is nothing further that he can add. He",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "further stated that he is certain this was not a mirage and that it actually",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "occurred.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "No further action is being taken by this office unless specified to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "do so by the Bureau.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
